WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:15.633
So the timeline I'm going to tell you the detail of what the Lord showed me when he came to me as a massive, fiery light, and the light was so bright.

00:00:15.634 --> 00:00:21.297
It literally felt like my spiritual eyes—my whole body—was melting.

00:00:21.298 --> 00:00:34.191
I literally said, "Lord, if you don't take and dim the light down and do something, I feel like it's going to kill me, like it's going to burn me up."And all of a sudden, because he knew it, he was so intense.

00:00:34.192 --> 00:00:46.549
And I'm telling you, in any intensity, I've never seen anything like this before in my life. He took something and he shielded himself.

00:00:46.550 --> 00:01:01.646
It was like a shield, and all of the light that was shining upon my face where it felt like it was blinding me, it came out the side of the shield.

00:01:01.647 --> 00:01:08.954
The light was still going, but it was being shaded and I could see up in it.

00:01:08.955 --> 00:01:26.082
And all of a sudden, a massive dove comes out of it with its wings flapping and an olive branch. It came over the top of me and the glory of the Lord filled me.

00:01:26.083 --> 00:01:50.992
And all of a sudden he said, "Brandon, I want to show you the time frame of humanity from the beginning of creation to where we are right now."And he showed me a thin line; it looked like a thread that went through the spans of humanity.

00:01:50.993 --> 00:02:00.010
It went from the beginning all the way to where we are. He divided it by thousand-year increments.

00:02:00.011 --> 00:02:12.359
It went 1,000 years, 2,000 years, 3,000 years, 4,000 years, 5,000 years, 6,000 years, and that's where we were. And then he divided it again into these little blocks.

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:29.999
So you could take a piece of paper and divide it out into a thousand, and then he divided in between those thousands by hundreds, and then he divided it by tens. So for each year, I could see faces.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:54.965
But I just want to say this: from the beginning of time, the dead in Christ—all of the believers that are in the dirt—it looked to me like there were millions of them.

00:02:54.966 --> 00:03:08.095
I could see their bones in the first couple layers of soil around the whole earth.

00:03:08.096 --> 00:03:21.335
There were skulls, hands, and legs; the bones of the believers were still in the dirt like fossilized remains.

00:03:21.336 --> 00:03:30.276
And they were looking in the spirit realm up toward the Father. The bones were a representation.

00:03:30.277 --> 00:03:34.228
I know "to be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord,"that's what the Bible says.

00:03:34.229 --> 00:03:57.276
But it was like they were looking up in the spirit realm waiting for the "dead in Christ will rise first."And I could see the anticipation in the earth waiting for the Son of Man to come at the rapture of the church, waiting for the coming of the Lord.

00:03:57.277 --> 00:04:08.931
The ground was anticipating. The bones were anticipating, kind of like "Can these bones live?"like it talks about in the Bible.

00:04:08.932 --> 00:04:21.553
The bones were anticipating the glory, and there was an atmosphere of acceleration and excitement in the bones.

00:04:21.554 --> 00:04:29.242
I don't know how; it's just what I saw. So he said, "I want to—"and this was something I did not want to skip.

00:04:29.243 --> 00:04:36.216
That was so important for you all to hear this: the dead in Christ are going to rise first and we are going to be all caught up with him.

00:04:36.217 --> 00:04:48.384
Watch what is about to happen, folks. I am so excited about it. Jesus is coming! It's so exciting.

00:04:48.385 --> 00:04:53.542
People have talked about this for generations and we're right there.

00:04:53.543 --> 00:05:03.391
The Lord even told me, "Brandon, I told you there will be a generation that will not taste death and you are that generation.

00:05:03.392 --> 00:05:10.786
You will be that generation that does not taste death."Wow.

00:05:10.787 --> 00:05:14.911
That's you! You're still here. I believe there's a remnant of you.

00:05:14.912 --> 00:05:23.673
I know there's probably some elderly people that'll probably go home, but I'm telling you, there is a generation that will not taste death.

00:05:23.674 --> 00:05:33.959
We will be the ones that are caught up. Glory to God! And we will see the soon return of our King.

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:44.972
So whenever he took me on the timeline and he took me by year, it was like he could fast forward it on a DVD player or a VCR.

00:05:44.973 --> 00:05:58.939
I know people don't use VCRs now, but like a recorder where you could speed it up, and I could see the years panning out, moving really fast in front of my face like building Legos.

00:05:58.940 --> 00:06:11.964
In each one, I could see the faces of the people that were ruling in that time going back. But he starts it out speaking the world into existence.

00:06:11.965 --> 00:06:21.999
And whenever he spoke the earth, I saw the earth come right before me like a ball of clay.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:28.968
A massive brown ball of clay came right in front of me whenever he spoke it into existence.

00:06:28.969 --> 00:06:36.257
And it was without form and void, right? And darkness was on the face of the deep.

00:06:36.258 --> 00:06:42.525
It all happened right in front of my face. And he's allowing me to see it in the timeline.

00:06:42.526 --> 00:06:49.462
And it's a ball of clay. It was a massive brown and red ball of clay.

00:06:49.463 --> 00:07:04.879
And when he spoke to it, it started to form. But there were no continents. It was all one big landmass in one area.

00:07:04.880 --> 00:07:12.871
There wasn't like South America, North America, Asia, and all this; it was just one big thing.

00:07:12.872 --> 00:07:26.402
And I don't know how it all was divided, whether it was Noah's flood or whatever—which I believe was Noah's flood that caused all this land to be divided and to create different continents.

00:07:26.403 --> 00:07:33.598
But when it first started, it was a garden—a massive garden area.

00:07:33.599 --> 00:07:40.329
So then he takes me to the garden and I see Adam and he is ripped.

00:07:40.330 --> 00:07:47.753
He is not a plump looking dude like me. I'm still working on it.

00:07:47.754 --> 00:07:55.847
He has muscles and he has a black-looking beard and he's olive-skinned.

00:07:55.848 --> 00:08:06.998
I only saw his backside with the glory around him. He had no clothes on in the natural; he had a glory around him.

00:08:06.999 --> 00:08:20.485
But he had black hair and it went into his beard, and his black beard was perfect.

00:08:20.486 --> 00:08:32.079
The way he looked was amazing. His arms were ripped. He did not look deteriorated like how we look worn down.

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:36.067
A lot of people's bodies look worn down. His body was not dead.

00:08:36.068 --> 00:08:44.639
There was no death. So he had no death around him. His body was fit and he looked good.

00:08:44.640 --> 00:08:54.818
Like seriously, there was no decay until—and I'm looking at it now and I've thought about it all these days—there was no decay on him.

00:08:54.819 --> 00:09:04.159
He was not dying. That did not happen until after they bit the fruit. He was in a body that renewed itself and it was perfect.

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:23.738
So he was there and he was communicating to this big lizard-like looking dinosaur thing that was like a Jurassic Park massive long-neck looking dinosaur and he was communicating to this dinosaur.

00:09:23.739 --> 00:09:33.305
I could see him pointing his finger at this dinosaur and the dinosaur was looking down and was understanding what he was saying.

00:09:33.306 --> 00:09:43.150
Kind of like how we talk to our dogs or our cats or whatever. He was communicating to this massive dinosaur and it was looking down at him.

00:09:43.151 --> 00:09:56.600
And people say, "Well, I didn't think prehistoric ages were in the earth at that time or whatever, and dinosaurs and T-Rexes and all that stuff."Well, this lizard thing was—and I did not see any other dinosaurs.

00:09:56.601 --> 00:10:06.043
I just saw one thing—and that dinosaur was bending down and he was eating grass and leaves off the trees.

00:10:06.044 --> 00:10:16.546
But I noticed this: there was no death in the garden of trees. The trees were not deteriorating with old dead limbs.

00:10:16.547 --> 00:10:20.769
The leaves were not turning any kind of dead-looking colors.

00:10:20.770 --> 00:10:30.215
They were all perfect. There was nothing dying at all in the garden. Everything was amazing.

00:10:30.216 --> 00:10:42.954
The trees were not like these little—we have trees where we go, "Wow, those are big trees."No, these trees that I saw in the garden, you couldn't put your arms around them.

00:10:42.955 --> 00:10:48.695
They were ginormous trees, and they were huge. They went so high up.

00:10:48.696 --> 00:11:00.316
They were not like the little trees that we see now; if they're 50 stories high, they're massive.

00:11:00.317 --> 00:11:10.257
A redwood is huge—that's the biggest tree we know—but these trees were so huge, and there was no death in them.

00:11:10.258 --> 00:11:21.723
All the grass and the foliage was just beautiful. But this is what I noticed the most in this part of the vision that the Lord allowed me to see: the sky was alive.

00:11:21.724 --> 00:11:41.439
The atmosphere of the earth was alive, and it had a vibration to it; it was vibrating. I could feel it in the spirit when I was looking into it.

00:11:41.440 --> 00:11:49.886
What the Lord allowed me to feel was the energy, the vibration of the atmosphere above the Earth's canopy.

00:11:49.887 --> 00:12:01.103
It wasn't blue like it is right now; it was like our sunsets where you see pinks and oranges and all kinds of things.

00:12:01.104 --> 00:12:12.588
That's the way the canopy looked. It had a life to it; it was almost like a fog, but it wasn't a fog.

00:12:12.589 --> 00:12:25.222
It was like thick water. I don't know how else to say this, folks; it looked like water above the atmosphere.

00:12:25.223 --> 00:12:37.384
It was all beautiful. It was thick-looking, almost like a transparent, translucent atmosphere.

00:12:37.385 --> 00:12:55.919
It was like a slime, but I don't know how to say it because there was no structure to it; it wasn't a solid, but it was thick, like moisture.

00:12:55.920 --> 00:13:01.309
There is no way to describe it with words. You could see the stars through it.

00:13:01.310 --> 00:13:07.518
I could see lights through it, and you could see pinks and purples. It was beautiful.

00:13:07.519 --> 00:13:13.621
It was like the sun was shining off of it, making it alive and moving.

00:13:13.622 --> 00:13:19.886
Then I could see the birds, and these were birds that are not here anymore.

00:13:19.887 --> 00:13:30.339
There were different kinds of birds with massive wingspans flying around in the atmosphere in the garden.

00:13:30.340 --> 00:13:52.189
It was beautiful. The water that the dinosaur was drinking was clear and crystal, and there was no pollution. Then he takes me to another span of time.

00:13:52.190 --> 00:14:11.167
He said, "I'm going to show you the key mile markers in the timeframe of humanity."Then he showed me Noah building the ark.

00:14:11.168 --> 00:14:27.937
I noticed his nose. There was a man with a massive white beard, but his nose was ginormous.

00:14:27.938 --> 00:14:40.946
It sounds weird, but his nose was huge. He had gray hair, and he looked like he had a hat on, like in Lord of the Rings.

00:14:40.947 --> 00:14:58.359
The people around him were all dark-looking and evil. Their countenances were dirty, like real dirt or grease.

00:14:58.360 --> 00:15:14.019
There were people behind him, and the Lord showed me this one man very clearly, with a big nose and body features.

00:15:14.020 --> 00:15:23.659
I could see the ark, and it was in a garden-type scenario; everything around it was really big, green, and beautiful.

00:15:23.660 --> 00:15:41.119
I didn't see a lot of things that looked bad. I know Eve had eaten the fruit by then, but the earth didn't look deteriorated from what I could see.

00:15:41.120 --> 00:16:02.931
Then he takes me to another part of time, and I see the pyramids and the Sphinx being built.

00:16:02.932 --> 00:16:17.915
They were using wood, ramps, pulleys, and all kinds of things to build these monuments.

00:16:17.916 --> 00:16:26.052
I didn't see any giants; I saw men working, like the Egyptians.

00:16:26.053 --> 00:16:46.135
Then he takes me to another timeframe, and I see the Roman Colosseum and the great Pantheon being built.

00:16:46.136 --> 00:16:51.990
I could see it being built like Legos, moving in front of my face.

00:16:51.991 --> 00:17:09.998
I could see Caesar Augustus, the Roman emperor, with a white robe and a laurel wreath on his head, watching over things.

00:17:09.999 --> 00:17:22.683
The history of the Roman emperors was being fast-forwarded in front of me.

00:17:22.684 --> 00:17:42.552
Then the Lord allowed me to see the Great Wall of China being built, stretching out over Asia.

00:17:42.553 --> 00:17:55.957
I saw wars happening, thousands of years of time passing in seconds.

00:17:55.958 --> 00:18:09.662
I could slow it down in the spirit realm, taking glimpses like photos.

00:18:09.663 --> 00:18:15.820
The Lord showed me Asian men riding horseback, fighting wars with swords, bows, arrows, and spears.

00:18:15.821 --> 00:18:37.657
They looked like samurai warriors. Then the Lord showed me Christopher Columbus sailing across the ocean to discover America.

00:18:37.658 --> 00:19:14.282
I could see him on the ship; he had long hair. Then he showed me World War I and World War II, and the acceleration of war.

00:19:14.283 --> 00:19:54.133
The birthing pains started in the early 1900s, and knowledge has increased with flight, jets, cars, electricity, and telecommunications, just as promised in the Bible.

00:19:54.134 --> 00:20:07.119
Then he stopped and said, "This is where you are right now. Adam's lease is up.

00:20:07.120 --> 00:20:14.849
Satan knows when Adam's lease is up. Son, it will happen on Rosh Hashanah.

00:20:14.850 --> 00:20:24.184
That's when the lease will be up."And I saw Satan moving like a snake throughout the earth.

00:20:24.185 --> 00:20:33.975
He went to talk to the pope and was communicating to key figures in the earth and Europe, which I don't understand.

00:20:33.976 --> 00:20:43.499
Like I said in this last video, I don't understand why he wasn't trying to communicate to people in America, but he was in Europe and in the Middle East talking to the key figures.

00:20:43.500 --> 00:20:54.519
And I've told you who I believe the Antichrist is: MBS. It's just who I believe I've seen as MBS.

00:20:54.520 --> 00:21:05.778
So, all that to say this, the Lord said, "Brandon, the devil was saying, 'You've got to give me my time now.

00:21:05.779 --> 00:21:14.959
Adam's lease is over, and you've got to give me my time to do my seven years of tribulation.'"And he was petitioning.

00:21:14.960 --> 00:21:21.467
And I heard the Lord say, "I have never been defeated. I will not be defeated now.

00:21:21.468 --> 00:21:28.263
I can control time."And he was telling Satan basically to go take a hike. "I'm controlling time.

00:21:28.264 --> 00:21:39.037
A day is a thousand years unto me."And he said, "And I can take a sliver of this time right here."And it was just like a little fraction, like a hair.

00:21:39.038 --> 00:21:45.330
You pull a hair out—well, not on my head—but you pull a hair out and you would be able to stretch it out.

00:21:45.331 --> 00:21:50.160
And that's how much of a sliver of time we had left to get a revival done.

00:21:50.161 --> 00:21:57.678
It was like the thickness of a hair—that thin. But he said, "That's all I need, Brandon.

00:21:57.679 --> 00:22:04.222
That's all I need."He said, "A great revival can happen in that sliver of a time.

00:22:04.223 --> 00:22:17.900
And we will have a great massive harvest of souls, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force."Well, I told you the angel armies were coming out of heaven to help us.

00:22:17.901 --> 00:22:23.599
But this is where it was: He no longer had to move in this time frame.

00:22:23.600 --> 00:22:28.959
When this happens, he no longer has to move through Adam's lease.

00:22:28.960 --> 00:22:36.296
Adam gave the earth to the son of man, but Adam committed high treason, messed up, and gave it to the devil.

00:22:36.297 --> 00:22:52.079
Then Jesus took it back, but it was still a lease—a covenant, I guess is what I want to call it, with man—that he would be able to reign for 6,000 years.

00:22:52.080 --> 00:23:00.128
When that time frame is over, we go into the thousand-year reign with Jesus Christ. So God had made that with man.

00:23:00.129 --> 00:23:14.586
And when that time frame is up, there will be a glory because the Lord said to me, "Brandon, people only see two sides of me and I'm multifaceted.

00:23:14.587 --> 00:23:23.036
They see the grace and they see the judgment, but I'm much more than that."There was a deepness to the Lord that people don't understand.

00:23:23.037 --> 00:23:45.666
And he said, "Brandon, I'm going to do so much in that little sliver of time, the outpouring there's going to be—whether that is a year, two years, or three years, I don't know."All I know is the glorious outpouring, the glorious church that he moves through unhindered by Adam's lease, will be something to be seen.

00:23:45.667 --> 00:23:52.973
We've never seen it before because all we've known is Adam's lease for 6,000 years.

00:23:52.974 --> 00:23:56.781
But we're going to see a side of God that we've never seen before.

00:23:56.782 --> 00:24:09.211
The great wells of revival, the great healing ministries that we saw in the early 1900s with Jack Coe, A.A.

00:24:09.212 --> 00:24:16.319
Allen, Smith Wigglesworth, William Branham, all the greats, Kathryn Kuhlman, all of them.

00:24:16.320 --> 00:24:28.989
We've only touched the very top surface, but we're about to see one of the greatest moves of God this planet has ever seen in a matter of just that much time.

00:24:28.990 --> 00:24:36.897
It's going to be a quick work. But Jesus is about to show us who he really is in this earth and in his body.

00:24:36.898 --> 00:24:42.772
And all the seeds that we've sowed in the past, I'm telling you, will come to harvest at last.

00:24:42.773 --> 00:24:47.179
We're going to see a great transfer of wealth from the sinner laid up for the righteous.

00:24:47.180 --> 00:24:52.507
And we're going to see a great harvest of souls and great healings and demonstrations manifest.

00:24:52.508 --> 00:24:56.371
God's going to show himself real to the Jews and to his church.

00:24:56.372 --> 00:25:01.110
And I'm telling you, your unsaved loved ones are coming home.

00:25:01.111 --> 00:25:05.594
Your unsaved loved ones are coming to Jesus Christ. It's time.

00:25:05.595 --> 00:25:14.185
They will, if you petition and pray for them—I'm telling you—they will come to the saving knowledge of Jesus Christ.

00:25:14.186 --> 00:25:22.394
There will be a move of God, and it will be such that people are just going to have to flatly put their head in the sand if they don't want to see what's about to happen.

00:25:22.395 --> 00:25:34.177
Yes, there's darkness and yes, there's wars and rumors of wars, but the body of Christ is going to move as an army and you're going to see it. I believe with all my heart and we're right there.

00:25:34.178 --> 00:25:51.630
Whether it happens today and we're stepping over into it or we start to see it—he shows me when you're looking in the spirit it looks like it's right on top of you, like it's going to happen tomorrow.

00:25:51.631 --> 00:26:01.996
But there's a depth perception when you're looking in the spirit, and so sometimes that could be a five-year window, a two-day thing, or whatever.

00:26:01.997 --> 00:26:11.275
I don't try to put a time frame on the Holy Spirit in visions anymore because it gets you in trouble.

00:26:11.276 --> 00:26:16.763
Like I said, you're looking in the spirit and it looks like it's right there, but there's depth perception.

00:26:16.764 --> 00:26:32.367
So, I'm learning, and it's a part of growing on my part, knowing that what seems imminent on your time could be a year from now or it could be right now.

00:26:32.368 --> 00:26:41.471
It's something we have to pray about. Just pray with me. But all I know is the Lord keeps talking to me and telling me he's coming, and he wants me to come on here and tell you all.

00:26:41.472 --> 00:26:54.317
He said, "Brandon, this will be fun. This is going to be fun."So, Father, I just thank you for every single person that is represented here today.

00:26:54.318 --> 00:26:59.918
We're believing for miracles. We're believing for the impossible.

00:26:59.919 --> 00:27:05.015
We're believing, Father, that this is the time of the great harvest.

00:27:05.016 --> 00:27:11.719
We call in healings and people being whole and healed and well in their bodies.

00:27:11.720 --> 00:27:19.710
Father, I thank you that you're the great physician, that every person who has a need is met.

00:27:19.711 --> 00:27:27.715
And that, Father, you heal every single person that is represented here today from the top of their head to the soles of their feet.

00:27:27.716 --> 00:27:33.498
We speak to the bodies and we call them healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

00:27:33.499 --> 00:27:41.114
Delivered from satanic bondage, from depression, anxiety, fear, worry, and torment of all kinds, including mental torment.

00:27:41.115 --> 00:27:55.152
Father, we thank you, Lord, that they're healed and whole and well from PTSD to Alzheimer's to dementia to autism to all of it.

00:27:55.153 --> 00:28:02.287
I mean, Lord, there's so many needs, there's so many things, but I know, Lord, that you took it all for us.

00:28:02.288 --> 00:28:21.150
And we thank you, Father, that no cancers, no diabetes, no heart disease, no strokes, no birthing problems, colon cancers, colon problems, or constipation issues—it all stems from the curse.

00:28:21.151 --> 00:28:28.079
But Galatians says that Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

00:28:28.080 --> 00:28:31.554
And I believe, Father, that they're healed by your stripes.

00:28:31.555 --> 00:28:36.393
And we call them healed and whole and well right now in the name of Jesus.

00:28:36.394 --> 00:28:47.578
And I believe with you that today, not tomorrow, not the next day—like my little girl says—but today Megan is healed.

00:28:47.579 --> 00:28:54.942
Today, your child is healed. Today, your manifestation and demonstration is happening.

00:28:54.943 --> 00:29:05.631
I believe that for you now. Satan, I tell you to get your hands off of God's stuff. I call forth finances in the name of Jesus.

00:29:05.632 --> 00:29:17.712
For every person who's believing for finances, I call their harvest in from the north, the south, the east, the west—some 30, some 60, and 100-fold depending on the ground you've sowed into.

00:29:17.713 --> 00:29:22.778
Now, Father, I thank you, Lord, for supernatural ideas to get wealth.

00:29:22.779 --> 00:29:30.475
I thank you, Father, that you said in your word that you would supply all their needs according to your riches in glory by Christ Jesus.

00:29:30.476 --> 00:29:34.372
I thank you, Lord, that they're the head and not the tail, above and not beneath.

00:29:34.373 --> 00:29:40.046
They'll go through and they'll not go under. This is a time of great acceleration of finances.

00:29:40.047 --> 00:29:46.020
I thank you, Lord, for blessing, increase, multiplication, and favor—whatever they need.

00:29:46.021 --> 00:29:52.911
Father, I thank you that you provide for it right now. I thank you, and we give you all the glory, honor, and praise for it.

00:29:52.912 --> 00:30:01.851
We thank you, Lord. We are expecting the manifestation to come. We're expecting it, and we give you praise, Father.

00:30:01.852 --> 00:30:08.985
Thank you, Lord, that you're bringing it to pass—a harvest at last. Amen and amen.

00:30:08.986 --> 00:30:13.359
Well, if this video blessed you today, I know it was something different.

00:30:13.360 --> 00:30:18.798
I tried not to have everything always be serious, but I wanted to tell you more about what the Lord showed me.

00:30:18.799 --> 00:30:30.270
